---
title: Crumbed Chicken Dippers & Rosemary Kumara Wedges with Garlic Aioli & Garden Salad
description: We’re officially making chicken (dippers) tonight, so don’t be afraid to break out your best chicken dance! We
recommend drizzling over the delicious garlic aioli, but these are called dippers, so if you need to grab ’em and dunk ’em, we won’t tell anyone. Promise.
